text.jpText: 芝と砂と キミの追い切りメニュー
text.enText: On the grass, on the sand, to your pre-race training menu

text.jpText: Turn Up! (Turn Up!) 声出せ叫べ (Wo oh oh)
text.enText: Turn up! (Turn up!) Raise your voice, shout out loud (wo oh oh)

text.jpText: トレセーン！ ファイ！ (オー！) ファイ！ (オー！)
text.enText: Tracen! Fight! (Ooh) Fight! (Ooh!)

text.jpText: たかたった 全力上がりタイム
text.enText: Takataktak · Wanna beat my time as hard as I can

text.jpText: ゆずれない夢の途中 (Wow Wow)
text.enText: On my way to a dream I won't yield (wow wow)

text.jpText: 始めよう ここから最高STORY (Wow Wow Wow)
text.enText: Start it right here, my own greatest story (Wow wow wow)

text.jpText: (o oh o oh…おっおっおーー！)
あこがれの地へ (勇気すこし借りて)
text.enText: To the place that I long for \n(Borrowing my courage just a bit)

text.jpText: 語り合ったMEMORY (二度と来ない今を)
text.enText: One precious shared memory \n(The right now we won't see back again)

text.jpText: もう ドキドキもトキメキも
text.enText: Oh, these bump-a-bumps and them thump-a-thumps

text.jpText: 抑えられない たまんない
text.enText: No I can't contain, can't get enough

text.jpText: 熱いハラハラが止まらない
text.enText: These strong tinglings just don't wanna stop

text.jpText: キミと 走り競いゴール目指し 遥か響け届けMUSIC
text.enText: With you I · run to the finish striving all the way \nFar and wide they will hear this music

text.jpText: ずっとずっとずっとずっと想い 夢がきっと叶うなら
text.enText: Forever ever ever ever in my thoughts \nIf my dream will be within reach soon

text.jpText: あの日キミに感じた何かを信じて
text.enText: I'll believe in what I felt that day \nThe special thing you held in you

text.jpText: 春も夏も秋も冬も超え 願い焦がれ走れ
text.enText: Overcoming springs 'n summers 'n autumns 'n winters \nWishing, and yearning, and running…

text.jpText: Ah 勝利へ
text.enText: To · victory
